hands_on_practices.solution:
我们从包含物质和辐射的平坦宇宙的弗里德曼方程开始，
$$\biggl(\frac{\dot a}{a}\biggr)^2 = H_0^2\bigl(\Omega_{m,0}a^{-3} + \Omega_{r,0}a^{-4}\bigr)\,. $$

1. 通过求解 $\rho_m=\rho_r$ 来找到物质-辐射相等时的标度因子 $a_{eq}$：
$$\rho_{m,0}a_{eq}^{-3}=\rho_{r,0}a_{eq}^{-4}
\;\Longrightarrow\;
a_{eq}=\frac{\rho_{r,0}}{\rho_{m,0}}
=\frac{\Omega_{r,0}}{\Omega_{m,0}}\,. $$

2. 宇宙时作为 $a$ 的函数是
$$t(a)=\int_0^a\frac{da'}{\dot a'}
=\frac1{H_0}\int_0^a\frac{da'}{a'\sqrt{\Omega_{m,0}a'^{-3}+\Omega_{r,0}a'^{-4}}}\,. $$
化简被积函数可得：
$$t(a)=\frac1{H_0}\int_0^a\frac{a'\,da'}{\sqrt{\Omega_{m,0}a'+\Omega_{r,0}}}\,. $$

3. 计算 $t_{eq} = t(a_{eq})$ 的积分。我们换元 $u=\Omega_{m,0}a'+\Omega_{r,0}$，则 $du=\Omega_{m,0}da'$。积分下限为 $a'=0 \to u=\Omega_{r,0}$，积分上限为 $a'=a_{eq} \to u=\Omega_{m,0}a_{eq}+\Omega_{r,0} = \Omega_{m,0}(\frac{\Omega_{r,0}}{\Omega_{m,0}})+\Omega_{r,0}=2\Omega_{r,0}$。我们还有 $a'=\frac{u-\Omega_{r,0}}{\Omega_{m,0}}$。
$$t_{eq}=\frac1{H_0\Omega_{m,0}^2}\int_{\Omega_{r,0}}^{2\Omega_{r,0}}
\frac{u-\Omega_{r,0}}{\sqrt{u}}\,du = \frac1{H_0\Omega_{m,0}^2}\int_{\Omega_{r,0}}^{2\Omega_{r,0}} (u^{1/2}-\Omega_{r,0}u^{-1/2})\,du\,. $$

4. 计算定积分：
$$
\int(u^{1/2}-\Omega_{r,0}u^{-1/2})du
=\frac{2}{3}u^{3/2}-2\Omega_{r,0}u^{1/2}
$$
$$
\Bigl[\frac{2}{3}u^{3/2}-2\Omega_{r,0}u^{1/2}\Bigr]_{\Omega_{r,0}}^{2\Omega_{r,0}}
= \left(\frac{2}{3}(2\Omega_{r,0})^{3/2} - 2\Omega_{r,0}(2\Omega_{r,0})^{1/2}\right) - \left(\frac{2}{3}\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2} - 2\Omega_{r,0}\Omega_{r,0}^{1/2}\right)
$$
$$
= \left(\frac{4\sqrt{2}}{3} - 2\sqrt{2}\right)\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2} - \left(\frac{2}{3} - 2\right)\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}
= \left(-\frac{2\sqrt{2}}{3} + \frac{4}{3}\right)\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2} = \frac{4-2\sqrt{2}}{3}\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}\,.
$$

5. 因此，
$$t_{eq}
=\frac1{H_0\Omega_{m,0}^2}\,\frac{4-2\sqrt2}{3}\,\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}
=\frac{2(2-\sqrt2)}{3H_0}\,\frac{\Omega_{r,0}^{3/2}}{\Omega_{m,0}^2}\,. $$
